data.title: Algeria Money Supply: M2: M1: Currency in Circulation
data.meta_description: Algeria Money Supply: M2: M1: Currency in Circulation data was reported at 7,392.800 DZD bn in Dec 2022. This records a decrease from the previous number of 7,427.300 DZD bn for Nov 2022. Algeria Money Supply: M2: M1: Currency in Circulation data is updated monthly, averaging 3,657.100 DZD bn (Median) from Jun 2006 to Dec 2022, with 199 observations. The data reached an all-time high of 7,427.300 DZD bn in Nov 2022 and a record low of 969.100 DZD bn in Jun 2006. Algeria Money Supply: M2: M1: Currency in Circulation data remains active status in CEIC and is reported by Bank of Algeria. The data is categorized under Global Database’s Algeria – Table DZ.KA001: Money Supply and Monetary Base.
